27#ifndef __LIBARCHIVE_BUILD
28#error This header is only to be used internally to libarchive.
29#endif
30
31#ifndef ARCHIVE_XXHASH_H
32#define ARCHIVE_XXHASH_H
33
34typedef enum { XXH_OK=0, XXH_ERROR } XXH_errorcode;
35
36struct archive_xxhash {
37 unsigned int (*XXH32)(const void* input, unsigned int len,
38 unsigned int seed);
39 void* (*XXH32_init)(unsigned int seed);
40 XXH_errorcode (*XXH32_update)(void* state, const void* input,
41 unsigned int len);
42 unsigned int (*XXH32_digest)(void* state);
43};
44
45extern const struct archive_xxhash __archive_xxhash;
46
47#endif
